      <div class="inner"> 
        
          <h1>Undergraduate Program</h1>

<hr>
<p>The undergraduate division of the Department of Mathematics offers a wide variety of courses in pure and applied mathematics taught by a distinguished faculty with a tradition of excellence in teaching and research.  Most of the faculty is associated with the University’s Courant Institute of Mathematical Sciences, noted for its advanced training and research programs.</p>

<ul>
	<li><a href="/dynamic/undergrad/overview/why-study-math/">Why study Math?</a></li>
	<li><a href="/dynamic/undergrad/overview/admissions/">Admissions</a></li>
</ul>

